original_title: New World Order: The Shadow Of Power
overview: Are we all just puppets on a string being manipulated by a secret cult with a greater plan known as the New World Order? Delve into the subject of true power and who holds it in this no-holds-bar documentary film. Unravel the mystery that continues to fascinate and mystify. Find out what the New World Order realy is and who is really in control. It's New World Order: Shadow of Power.
title: New World Order: The Shadow Of Power
